Class ModifyPart

java.lang.Object
Controller.ModifyPart
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyPart extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class displays and controls the Modify Part Screen. Navigate to this page from the Main Menu. This class allow the user to change and update the fields of a selected Part.
